title: Ep. 413 - They’re Turning The Frickin’ Penguins Gay
description:
A London aquarium took a penguin chick from her parents to be raised genderless by two lesbian birds. Then, three pieces of great news all in a row for the Trump administration, bad news for Democrats. And finally, the Mailbag! Date: 09-12-2019
